### How It Works
- This code generates a calendar within a single HTML page.
- It highlights all the **Wednesdays** (day 3 of the week) in light blue color.
- The calendar automatically adjusts to show the current month each time the page is loaded.

### Usage
You can save this code as an HTML file (e.g., `calendar.html`) and open it in a web browser to see the calendar for the current month with all Wednesdays highlighted.
